    "Each topic contained ten key lexical items.",
    "These words are presented in descending order of association with the latent topic in Table 1.",
    "The number of topics was decided through manual topic inspection and regeneration, examining the ten key words each time, to ensure minimal lexical item overlap.We then presented the assignment of a topic to each tweet as a trajectory.",
